      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help, but it doesnt change the fact that i'm empty. it's like the pilot left the plane and now the machinery is just running on autopilot. it feels fake. if the art is what made me human, then what am i even doing here? just being a ghost in a living body?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
